{"type": "article", "id": 6911, "title": "INSTAMP 图章", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-28T07:47:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001021b9MhW0ewDALNuYv5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一位名为 Yuzo Azu 的日本设计师为我们带来的一款图章作品，近来在<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Designboom </a>与雷克萨斯举办的雷克萨斯全球设计大奖中被津津乐道。这些印章采用硅胶材料，通过调整角度和按压力度，同一个图章可以给我们带来完全不同的印制作品。这些图章的字体简洁美观，通过力度的控制甚至可以呈现东方书法的特色。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001019ZQWvwlPNIYB7ChMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;\"></span>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060010192xu7ot1Rza6EhGXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65036675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001020NGfxXPIK1kjheliE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"3.68215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}